content.rendered: Season’s Greetings! At the TTE headquarters, we embraced the festive vibes of Christmas with a simple yet joyful Secret Santa celebration. The Santas merrily joined in to play games, exchange gifts and create a warm atmosphere of togetherness. Here’s a glimpse of the joyous event!
